entries.femaleVariant: Solid work, V. Jasmine's on her way to her dearest husband, and I get my dearest eddies. Or should I say our eddies, huh?
V, you were supposed to get Jasmine to the ride. The chick's in shock – she doesn't know up from down! What if she made a wrong turn or-- Look, you're lucky she made it, OK?
Drill this into your skull for the future – a job's done when the client's secured. Process that – absorb it. It ain't hard to understand. Closing the gig.
Job well done, V. Closing the gig.
